title: Morning Joe 11/19/21
description: House Democrats postponed a much-anticipated vote on President Joe Biden's social safety net and climate package early Friday morning after Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy delayed a final vote with a record-long, wide-ranging and often angry speech.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
